{"tha-ap108:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap108:0.2":"Bhikkhadayivagga ","tha-ap108:0.3":"Udakapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap108:1.1":"“Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap108:1.2":"Gacchantam anilanjase; ","tha-ap108:1.3":"Ghatasanamva jalitam, ","tha-ap108:1.4":"Adittamva hutasanam. ","tha-ap108:2.1":"Panina udakam gayha, ","tha-ap108:2.2":"akase ukkhipim aham; ","tha-ap108:2.3":"Sampaticchi mahaviro, ","tha-ap108:2.4":"buddho karuniko isi. ","tha-ap108:3.1":"Antalikkhe thito sattha, ","tha-ap108:3.2":"padumuttaranamako; ","tha-ap108:3.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap108:3.4":"imam gatham abhasatha. ","tha-ap108:4.1":"‘Imina dakadanena, ","tha-ap108:4.2":"pitiuppadanena ca; ","tha-ap108:4.3":"Kappasatasahassampi, ","tha-ap108:4.4":"duggatim nupapajjati’. ","tha-ap108:5.1":"Tena kammena dvipadinda, ","tha-ap108:5.2":"lokajettha narasabha; ","tha-ap108:5.3":"Pattomhi acalam thanam, ","tha-ap108:5.4":"hitva jayaparajayam. ","tha-ap108:6.1":"Sahassarajanamena, ","tha-ap108:6.2":"tayo te cakkavattino; ","tha-ap108:6.3":"Pancasatthikappasate, ","tha-ap108:6.4":"caturanta janadhipa. ","tha-ap108:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap108:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap108:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap108:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma udakapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap108:9.1":"Udakapujakattherassapadanam chattham. "}